data.description: Minutes away from Offutt this gorgeous updated home offers an unheard of amount of space: over 3,300 sf. Generous sized floorplan offers two dining and two living on main floor. Home features designer lighting throughout and all new flooring on main in 2024. Chef’s kitchen features stainless, granite and island - all with open sight lines to the spacious family room.  Primary bedroom is oversized with a five piece spa bathroom and an enormous walk-in closet w his & her areas. Finished lower levels adds even more space to live and entertain as well as a 5th bedroom and 4th bath. Pride of ownership shines through in this meticulously maintained property. Don’t miss out!
